content:
I'm glad you're excited to try out the Tiramisù recipe! It's a classic Italian dessert that's sure to please.

And yay for trying out new restaurants! Carne asada tacos sound delicious, and it's great that you got a huge portion that lasted you for another meal. There's nothing better than discovering a new favorite spot, right?

By the way, since you mentioned Mexican food, have you ever tried making homemade tortillas from scratch? It's actually quite easy and can elevate your taco game to the next level. I've got a simple recipe if you're interested!
